  "content": "<p>Please follow the instructions to keep LetsVPN running in the background.</p><p>One of the features of MIUI is to optimize your battery, which means the task manager will kill background apps to save power. In order to keep your LetsVPN running all the time, please follow the instructions below.</p><ul style='list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 2rem; margin: 1rem 0;'><li>Choose \"No Restrictions\" in LetsVPN Background Settings</li><li>Go to Recent, then lock LetsVPN</li></ul><p>If you are using other mobile phones, please read <a href='/help/en/article/7' class='text-blue-600 hover:underline'>How to fix my unstable LetsVPN connection?</a></p><h2 style='margin-top:2rem;'>Background Settings</h2><p>Please follow the instructions presented on the gif. The setting for MIUI 9 and MIUI 10 is similar.</p><ol style='list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 2rem; margin: 1rem 0;'><li>Go to Settings, tap \"Manage apps\"</li><li>Tap LetsVPN, then tap Battery Saver</li><li>Select \"No Restrictions\" option</li></ol><img src='/assets/use-keepback-xiaomi-1.gif' alt='MIUI Background Settings' /><h2 style='margin-top:2rem;'>Lock LetsVPN</h2><h3>For MIUI 10 users,</h3><ol style='list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 2rem; margin: 1rem 0;'><li>Go to Recent</li><li>Tap and hold on LetsVPN</li><li>Tap \"Lock\" icon</li><li>You will see a \"lock\" displayed on the top right corner</li></ol><img src='/assets/use-keepback-xiaomi-2.gif' alt='Lock LetsVPN on MIUI 10' /><h3>For MIUI 9 users,</h3><ol style='list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 2rem; margin: 1rem 0;'><li>Go to Recent, then pull down LetsVPN icon to lock the app</li><li>You will see a \"lock\" displayed on the top right corner</li></ol><img src='/assets/use-keepback-xiaomi-3.gif' alt='Lock LetsVPN on MIUI 9' /><p style='margin-top:2rem;'>Now you can enjoy our \"Stay Connected All the Time\" service!</p><p>If none of the above solutions are helpful, please reach us at <a href='mailto:letsvpn@rbox.me' class='text-blue-600 hover:underline'>letsvpn@rbox.me</a>. Our customer support team is happy to assist you.</p><hr class='my-8 border-gray-200' /><div class='mt-8 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 shadow-sm'><h3 class='text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2'>Related Articles</h3><ul><li class='border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0'><a href='/help/en/article/8' class='flex justify-between items-center py-3 text-gray-700 hover:text-brand-purple transition-colors'><span class='text-base'>Keep LetsVPN running in the background (for Huawei users)</span><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='h-5 w-5 text-gray-400' viewBox='0 0 20 20' fill='currentColor'><path fill-rule='evenodd' d='M7.293 14.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L10.586 10 7.293 6.707a1 1 0 011.414-1.414l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z' clip-rule='evenodd' /></svg></a></li><li class='border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0'><a href='/help/en/article/32' class='flex justify-between items-center py-3 text-gray-700 hover:text-brand-purple transition-colors'><span class='text-base'>Keep LetsVPN running in the background (for Samsung users)</span><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='h-5 w-5 text-gray-400' viewBox='0 0 20 20' fill='currentColor'><path fill-rule='evenodd' d='M7.293 14.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L10.586 10 7.293 6.707a1 1 0 011.414-1.414l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z' clip-rule='evenodd' /></svg></a></li><li class='border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0'><a href='/help/en/article/7' class='flex justify-between items-center py-3 text-gray-700 hover:text-brand-purple transition-colors'><span class='text-base'>How to fix my unstable LetsVPN connection?</span><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='h-5 w-5 text-gray-400' viewBox='0 0 20 20' fill='currentColor'><path fill-rule='evenodd' d='M7.293 14.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L10.586 10 7.293 6.707a1 1 0 011.414-1.414l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z' clip-rule='evenodd' /></svg></a></li><li class='border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0'><a href='/help/en/article/44' class='flex justify-between items-center py-3 text-gray-700 hover:text-brand-purple transition-colors'><span class='text-base'>Special Settings for SmartByte</span><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='h-5 w-5 text-gray-400' viewBox='0 0 20 20' fill='currentColor'><path fill-rule='evenodd' d='M7.293 14.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L10.586 10 7.293 6.707a1 1 0 011.414-1.414l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z' clip-rule='evenodd' /></svg></a></li><li class='border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0'><a href='/help/en/article/3' class='flex justify-between items-center py-3 text-gray-700 hover:text-brand-purple transition-colors'><span class='text-base'>How to delete account in LetsVPN?</span><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='h-5 w-5 text-gray-400' viewBox='0 0 20 20' fill='currentColor'><path fill-rule='evenodd' d='M7.293 14.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L10.586 10 7.293 6.707a1 1 0 011.414-1.414l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z' clip-rule='evenodd' /></svg></a></li></ul></div><div class='mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200 text-center'><p class='text-gray-600 mb-4'>Did this answer your question?</p><div class='flex justify-center space-x-4 mt-2'><button class='text-4xl p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors' aria-label='Dissatisfied'>üòû</button><button class='text-4xl p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors' aria-label='Neutral'>üòê</button><button class='text-4xl p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors' aria-label='Satisfied'>üòÉ</button></div></div>"
